OL,3,CAmerica's 'special relationship' is
OL,4,C'probably Israel', says UK ambassador
OL,5,Cto US
OL,7,FThe UK's ambassador to the US has said
OL,8,Fthe only country that has a "special
OL,9,Frelationship" with America is
OL,10,F"probably Israel".
OL,12,FThe comments by Sir Christian Turner,
OL,13,Fpublished by the Financial Times,
OL,14,Fthreaten to embarrass the King during
OL,15,Fthis week's crucial state visit to the
OL,16,FUS, amid transatlantic tensions over
OL,17,Fthe Iran war.
OL,26,@pD@]OUqD@MO]rD@AOUrD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
