OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777464668
OL,3,CAmerica's 'special relationship' is
OL,4,C'probably Israel', says UK ambassador
OL,5,Cto US
OL,7,FThe Foreign Office has stressed the
OL,8,Ftop diplomat's remarks made to a group
OL,9,Fof visiting students in February were
OL,10,F"certainly not any reflection of the
OL,11,FUK government's position".
OL,13,FA recording of his comments was
OL,14,Fobtained by the FT this week.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
