PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777464668
OL,3,CAmerica's 'special relationship' is
OL,4,C'probably Israel', says UK ambassador
OL,5,Cto US
OL,7,FDuring a question-and-answer session,
OL,8,FSir Christian said he disliked the
OL,9,Fphrase "special relationship" to
OL,10,Fdescribe the US-UK ties and argued it
OL,11,Fwas "quite nostalgic, it's quite
OL,12,Fbackwards-looking, and it has a lot of
OL,13,Fbaggage about it".
OL,15,FHe added: "I think there is probably
OL,16,Fone country that has a special
OL,17,Frelationship with the United States -
OL,18,Fand that is probably Israel."
OL,26,@qD@HOUqD@]O]sD@EOUuD@QO]wD@KOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777464668
OL,3,CAmerica's 'special relationship' is
OL,4,C'probably Israel', says UK ambassador
OL,5,Cto US
OL,7,FHis remarks were made ahead of the US
OL,8,Fand Israel launching military strikes
OL,9,Fagainst Iran, triggering the current
OL,10,FMiddle East conflict.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FNevertheless, he said Britain's links
OL,18,Fto the US were "so strong", and added:
OL,19,F"There is a deep history and affinity
OL,20,Fbetween us. Particularly on defence
OL,21,Fand security, we are intertwined."
OL,26,@zD@POUzD@ZO]{D@AOU}D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
