PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777464668
OL,3,CAmerica's 'special relationship' is
OL,4,C'probably Israel', says UK ambassador
OL,5,Cto US
OL,7,FHe went on: "The relationship will
OL,8,Fcarry on, if you want, being
OL,9,F'special', but I think it's going to
OL,10,Fhave to be different."
OL,12,FSir Christian also said it was
OL,13,F"extraordinary" that the scandal over
OL,14,Fthe paedophile financier Jeffrey
OL,15,FEpstein, which has had far-reaching
OL,16,Fconsequences in the UK, "hasn't
OL,17,Ftouched anybody" in the US.
OL,26,@oD@MOUrD@VO]uD@AOUuD@OO]xD@YOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
