PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777464668
OL,3,CAmerica's 'special relationship' is
OL,4,C'probably Israel', says UK ambassador
OL,5,Cto US
OL,7,FIn contrast, he said the controversy
OL,8,Fhad "brought down" the former prince
OL,9,FAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor and Sir
OL,10,FChristian's predecessor in Washington,
OL,11,FLord Peter Mandelson.
OL,13,FSir Christian also said the future of
OL,14,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer had
OL,15,Fbeen "quite touch and go" over his
OL,16,Fappointment of the disgraced peer, and
OL,17,Fif Labour did badly in the upcoming
OL,18,Flocal elections, the party could
OL,19,F"remove him".
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@RO]wD@FOUwD@YO]{D@AOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
