PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777464668
OL,3,CAmerica's 'special relationship' is
OL,4,C'probably Israel', says UK ambassador
OL,5,Cto US
OL,7,FHis remarks were made public ahead of
OL,8,Fthe King's speech to Congress as part
OL,9,Fof his four-day royal visit to the US
OL,10,Fwith the Queen.
OL,12,FThere are hopes the trip could help
OL,13,Frepair relations between the two
OL,14,Fcountries after US President Donald
OL,15,FTrump's repeated criticism of the
OL,16,Fprime minister for refusing to join
OL,17,Fthe offensive against Tehran, branding
OL,18,Fhim weak and indecisive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
