PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777464668
OL,3,CAmerica's 'special relationship' is
OL,4,C'probably Israel', says UK ambassador
OL,5,Cto US
OL,7,FIn his address on Capitol Hill,
OL,8,FCharles will acknowledge the current
OL,9,Fstrained relations, pointing out that
OL,10,Fwhile the UK and US have disagreed at
OL,11,Ftimes during their long history, both
OL,12,Fnations "have always found ways to
OL,13,Fcome together".
OL,15,FHe is also expected to put recent
OL,16,Fdifficulties into context, saying "our
OL,17,Fdefence, intelligence and security
OL,18,Fties are measured not in years but in
OL,19,Fdecades".
OL,26,@tD@IOUuD@NO]xD@cOU{D@HO]
